    org.locationtech.jts.jump.workbench.driver  
    org.locationtech.jts.jump.workbench.model
    Layers, Categories, and Layer Managers -- the top level of abstraction in the JUMP data model, wrapping Features and FeatureCollections, which in turn wrap Geometries.
    org.locationtech.jts.jump.workbench.plugin
    The API for "plug-ins", which are code modules that can be assigned to buttons and menu items.
